      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BINNAWAY WARRIOR (7) produced a slick 16.76 when placed over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight last start in a Grade 5/6. Has the ability and expected to go close again. ZIPPING BOTHAM (1) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 9 lengths fourth (31.24) last time in a Grade 5 at this track over 530m. Gets chance to atone. PROCLIVITY (5) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at Murray Bridge Straight in a handy 16.54 beating Shiny Pistol. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. One of the prime contenders. NOVA'S FERN (3) continues to race well and is sure to be competitive again.",
